/* Headline "Max COB" */
"Max COB" = "Max COB";

/* "Max COB" */
"The default of maxCOB is 120. (If someone enters more carbs in one or multiple entries, iAPS will cap COB to maxCOB and keep it at maxCOB until the carbs entered above maxCOB have shown to be absorbed. Essentially, this just limits UAM as a safety cap against weird COB calculations due to fluky data.)" = "The default of maxCOB is 120. (If someone enters more carbs in one or multiple entries, iAPS will cap COB to maxCOB and keep it at maxCOB until the carbs entered above maxCOB have shown to be absorbed. Essentially, this just limits UAM as a safety cap against weird COB calculations due to fluky data.)";

